      • buildGraphs

        public void buildGraphs(boolean clean,
                        int startSec,
                        int endSec)
        Builds the graphs to display and puts them into the lines ArrayList.
        Parameters:
        clean - - true if you want to create graphs that are clean, false if you want precise values that can show gaps or overlaps
        startSec - - the seconds value to start graphing after the query start time
        endSec - - the seconds value to end graphing after the query start time
